181	      <p class="eyebrow">The field, ranked</p>
182	      <h2>Where each system lands.</h2>
183	      <p class="narrow">Every system here is scored by RACE, in which a GPT&#8209;5.5 model grades the quality of each report. Deep Cove Research is the highest&#8209;scoring self&#8209;hostable system on the board, and it ranks ahead of every closed model from the major AI labs. Two systems edge it at the top.</p>
