333	        <p class="cap">Grok&rsquo;s accuracy was just as high, at 91% &mdash; but it rested on only 10 citations, where a single miss would move the figure nine points. Deep Cove Research&rsquo;s 90.3% rests on 84 checked sources, a far sturdier base.</p>
